metadata.name: Jolly Elves Girls #127
metadata.description: The Jolly Elves have courageously volunteered to complete a perilous mission for their benefactor Santa. 6,000 Elves were handpicked to venture into the digital metaverse to discover new methods and techniques to get gifts to everyone throughout the year. The compliment to the Jolly Elves genesis collection of male elves has now arrived in the form of 3,000 female elves; the gift that keeps giving and a critical component to future utility.
